[I] A framework for searching and managing metadata

[T] Baloo is the file indexing and file search framework for KDE Plasma. It
[T] focuses on speed and a very small memory footprint. It maintains an index
[T] of your files and optionally their contents which you can search.

[U] https://www.kde.org

